'''''Poacher''''' ni [[Kenya|film ngufi ya Kenya]] / [[Ubwongereza]] yasohotse  2018 iyobowe na Tom Whitworth<ref>Locally shot short film Poacher to premier on Netflix today <nowiki>https://www.standardmedia.co.ke</nowiki> › arts-and-culture › lo...</ref>. Iyi filime yitabiriwe n'abantu benshi nyuma yo gusohoka muri Netflix muri Nzeri 2020<ref>Poacher movies | Best and New films <nowiki>https://bestsimilar.com</nowiki> › tag › 36939-poacher</ref>.  Yabaye kandi filime ya mbere yo muri Kenya yasohotse binyuze kuri Netflix<ref>Poacher | Netflix <nowiki>https://www.netflix.com</nowiki> › title</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Yakozwe mu buryo butangaje bwa firime, ''Poacher'' ivuga amateka y’umuhinzi wihebye uhura n’ibibazo nyuma yo kwiba igiti cy’amahembe y’inzovu mu gatsiko k’iterabwoba <ref>“Poacher” brings a trunk-load of storytelling to Netflix - Hagerty ... <nowiki>https://hagertyjourn.com</nowiki> › editorials › reviews › poache...</ref>. Iyi filime irashaka kwerekana ikibazo gikomeye mpuzamahanga cy’ubucuruzi bw’inzovu mu buryo butemewe hifashishijwe ibibazo by’abaturage, inzovu ziri mu kaga muri Afurika<ref>Kenya's Conservation Film 'Poacher' to Air on Netflix Sept.30 <nowiki>https://khusoko.com</nowiki> › 2020/09/03 › kenyas-conservati...</ref>. 

